ng\", \"from\": 7099, \"to\": 7116}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent reportthat\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7146}, {\"ngram\": \"a prescription heart drug\", \"from\": 7227, \"to\": 7252}, {\"ngram\": \"stamina\", \"from\": 7271, \"to\": 7278}, {\"ngram\": \"endurance\", \"from\": 7283, \"to\": 7292}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 7309, \"to\": 7321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Close friends were potentially impacted by WADA's failure to follow its own rules in investigating the nearly two dozen positive tests on Chinese swimmers,\\\" Phelps testified.\", \"from\": 7341, \"to\": 7516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7480, \"end\": 7487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9991398248366367, \"rank\": 0.0008497275437711954, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 7499, \"end\": 7505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9089823853783528e-12, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Close friends\", \"from\": 7342, \"to\": 7355}, {\"ngram\": \"WADA's failure\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7399}, {\"ngram\": \"its own rules\", \"from\": 7410, \"to\": 7423}, {\"ngram\": \"the nearly two dozen positive tests\", \"from\": 7441, \"to\": 7476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many of them will live with the 'what ifs' for the rest of their lives.\\\"\", \"from\": 7517, \"to\": 7590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 7565, \"to\": 7573}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 7577, \"to\": 7588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Schmitt was part of the U.S. 800-meter freestyle relay team that finished a close second to China during the Tokyo games.\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7684, \"end\": 7689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999818536412308, \"rank\": 1.7281267934509248e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 7701, \"end\": 7706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9997366834598707, \"rank\": 0.00026289242339585644, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Schmitt\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7599}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 7604, \"to\": 7608}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. 800-meter freestyle relay team\", \"from\": 7612, \"to\": 7651}, {\"ngram\": \"a close second\", \"from\": 7666, \"to\": 7680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We raced hard.\", \"from\": 7715, \"to\": 7730, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We trained hard.\", \"from\": 7731, \"to\": 7747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We followed every protocol,\\\" Schmitt testified Tuesday.\", \"from\": 7748, \"to\": 7803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every protocol\", \"from\": 7760, \"to\": 7774}, {\"ngram\": \"Schmitt\", \"from\": 7777, \"to\": 7784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We accepted our defeat with grace.\", \"from\": 7804, \"to\": 7839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our defeat\", \"from\": 7817, \"to\": 7827}, {\"ngram\": \"grace\", \"from\": 7833, \"to\": 7838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of us will be haunted by this podium finish that may have been impacted by doping.\\\"\", \"from\": 7840, \"to\": 7928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 7848, \"to\": 7850}, {\"ngram\": \"this podium finish\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7888}, {\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 7920, \"to\": 7926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chinese officials blamed the banned substance on contaminated food at the athletes' hotel.\", \"from\": 7930, \"to\": 8020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7930, \"end\": 7937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9991398248366367, \"rank\": 0.0008497275437711954, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the banned substance\", \"from\": 7955, \"to\": 7975}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 7992, \"to\": 7996}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' hotel\", \"from\": 8000, \"to\": 8019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The banned drug, which is only available in pill form, somehow ended up in the kitchen of a hotel the swimmers were staying at,\\\" said Rep. Cathy McMorris Rodgers, R-Wash., who is also the chair of the Energy and Commerce Committee, as she questioned how WADA could conclude \\\"this explanation was plausible.\\\"\", \"from\": 8022, \"to\": 8330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8162, \"end\": 8184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathy_McMorris_Rodgers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cathy McMorris Rodgers\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathy_McMorris_Rodgers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathy_McMorris_Rodgers\"}, {\"begin\": 8235, \"end\": 8253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_House_Committee_on_Energy_and_Commerce\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.334059194207125e-53, \"text\": \"Commerce Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_House_Committee_on_Energy_and_Commerce\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_House_Committee_on_Energy_and_Commerce\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The banned drug\", \